name: Cat Photos
description:
This doc, that doc, the other doc, blah blah blah. It blends together with the hum of the florescent lights to gently lull you into a daze. ü•±

But then you see it, right next to Q3 earning projects: a cute cat photo! üò∏ For a brief moment you feel joy again, all thanks to the Cat Photos Pack!

Use this Pack to easily add cat photos to your docs, with a few different options:

2Ô∏è‚É£ A "Cat Photo" column type. Apply this to a column in any Coda table and the text you enter into that column will be overlaid on top of a random cat photo. How fun!

3Ô∏è‚É£ A "Cats" Pack table that lists every cat photo available, along with relevant metadata.
